user.bio:
Epic Fanboy ✔️ 
Spending too much money on beer ✔️ 
Sucker for a hoppy IIPA ✔️
Loves craft beer / PINT / games / movies / running / proud dad ! Check-ins with year : *seasonal or mentioned on label*
...and then Beer said "put that on Facebook, it's hilarious!"  But Beer was wrong; so very wrong.
Amateur beer taster looking to go pro.
